attributes.title: Disappointed
attributes.review: As soon as I opened the app, a message popped up calling me the f-slur. I thought maybe this was a glitch so I continued into the app. About 10-15 seconds later, a new pop up appeared on the screen that called me the n-word with a very strange, racist photo. I thought maybe it was just a blip in the apps coding, but then a few seconds later, a new message popped up that called me the t-slur, followed by the k-slur (the anti-Semitic one) and then a very high quality image of what appeared to be a piece of poop in a toilet bowl. That’s when I knew something was up. I tried to leave the app, but when trying to press the home button, a message popped up saying “there’s no escaping your cage, immigrant”. I had no choice but to hard reset my phone. Definitely do not recommend.
